'''Nasser Qassim Al Qasabi''' ({{lang-ar|ناصر قاسم القصبي}}) is a [[Saudi Arabia]]n [[actor]]. He started his acting career in 1984 and is known for his various roles in the series ''[[Tash Ma Tash|No Big Deal]]'' ([[Arabic]]: طاش ما طاش<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.waleg.com/archives/017438.html|title=The Return of Tash 16 on MBC|date=August 11, 2009|work=Waleg|accessdate=25 May 2011}}</ref>) In 2012, Nasser became one of the three judges on the television series, ''[[Arabs Got Talent]]''.
Al Qasbi has featured in a Saudi TV show satirising [[ISIL]] called ''Selfie''.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2015/06/22/middleeast/anti-isis-satire/index.html|title=Saudi TV series deploys new weapon against ISIS: satire|work=CNN|date=22 Jun 2015}}</ref>
